{
  "stem": "3820.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Actually, I didn't want her to leave.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I guess she was my anchor for those couple years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But she left during the night when I was asleep.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So there was no goodbye, goodbye.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "During the couple of days that she stayed, she said that my uncle had come for me, that I was going to live with him now.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she couldn't leave all the animals alone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, you know, and I would go to school and things like that, where there was no school on the farm.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But she left when I was asleep, so I don't know whether I would have caused a scene or not.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I do.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm sorry that the circumstances made it so that I cannot remember her last name if it was ever told to me, that I couldn't write to her to say thank you for her care of me, to maybe help her in some way, you know, not exactly the way she helped me but somehow do something.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I don't know how.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I've wished her well all my life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would like to say thank you very much for taking me in, for caring for me, for doing the few little things that she had the time to do with me-- the walks, the showing me how to feed the chickens, the, the bathing, the taking care, the things that a child needs from a grownup.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I appreciate all that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know if she came right out and told me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know that she said that my mother and father had told me that they would be back in a while, but circumstances were such that they couldn't come back.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I think that from what she said, I knew because we knew.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
